{"tid":56370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩慘得過比娘娘話「我地唔係情侶黎架」","createTime":"2016-12-27T07:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T08:26:49.000Z","uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"957722ae40a8622b0eea2d2d9e0c987ef97188f4","tid":56370,"uid":37825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的 頭先諗住幫兩個客影相 <br />\n點知個女仔話「哦，唔使喇，我地唔係情侶黎架」<br />\n我嗰陣呆左啦 之後心諗 係朋友都可以一齊影張相架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到咁其實都真係幾似收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果到依家都仲係見到佢地互相幫對方影單人照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我又想問 唔熟嘅一男一女會唔會一齊去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想咁先入為主咁認為佢地係娘娘同兵嘅關係<br />\n但除此之外我實在睇唔透仲會有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa743a4ad8c9ea1e80473b823fb2ba108f89c3c","tid":56370,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"我地一世都係好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07d97c36b7a4e584e120b0743c9f1b2f0a98301","tid":56370,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"可能係炮友呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a48d1d0f11bbc35cde23799c3d2b16cece7bcc","tid":56370,"uid":53597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:07:39.000Z","msg":"不是男朋友卻比男朋友更親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb1081d0e45c5b3162a18ad80e2c314f89e5d33","tid":56370,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"